(17, 'Uniflow: Metallic Stearates', 'uniflow', '<p>We are the largest and most technically sound manufacturers of stearates in India, with an installed capacity of 5000 tons/month, offering our proprietary DLI grades made using a fusion process that combines the good properties of wet process precipitated stearates with thermal stability. Available in powder and granules form. Our products have standout features like low moisture, minimal free fatty acids, clear appearance when melted, no heavy metals, and low salt levels. Our catalogue includes Zinc, calcium, Aluminium, Barium, Potassium, Sodium, Magnesium, Lithium and cadmium stearates. Aqueous solutions available for calcium and zinc as well.</p>\r\n', 'uploads/67868a0a17030_uniflow-logo.webp', '2024-05-29 12:28:14', '2025-05-20 14:40:35', 'Published', 'uploads/66f16999288ac_meta.jpg', '<h2>Applications:</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Largely used in the Rubber and plastic industry as lubricant. It has many other applications which include:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Paints- Zinc stearate is used as a thickener to form paste with solvents | Calcium stearate is used for its water repellent nature in cement paints | Aluminum stearate for its anti-settling nature.</li>\r\n	<li>Pharma- Magnesium stearate for tablet coating.</li>\r\n	<li>Cosmetics</li>\r\n	<li>Construction chemicals</li>\r\n	<li>SMC and BMC, fibre composites<br />\r\n	&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', 'uploads/66f16999289f8_poly.jpg', 1, 'High-Performance Plastic & Polymer Additives | MLA Group', 'Get premium Uniflow zinc, calcium, & magnesium stearates from MLA Group. Ideal for rubber, paints, pharma, cosmetics, construction, & fibre composites for Industries.\r\n'),
(18, 'Unicell: Foaming Agents', 'unicell', '<p>ADC is a yellow coloured powder which is used as a blowing agent/foaming agent to release gas to form a uniform gas matrix of entrapped gas inside the polymer in which it is mixed, giving a foam/sponge effect when the polymer mix containing ADC is heated during processing. ADC despite being yellow in colour gives a white decomposition residue and hence does not impart any colour to the vulcanized product, nor any odour.&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'uploads/685d4c07cdb0a_unicell-foaming-agent.webp', '2024-05-29 12:29:15', '2025-06-26 13:32:55', 'Published', 'uploads/66f173540c774_adc.jpg', '<h2>Applications</h2>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>EVA/LD rubber blocks, sheets and footwear.</li>\r\n	<li>Vinyl flooring</li>\r\n	<li>Leather cloths and sheets, wall paper</li>\r\n	<li>Foamboard or WPC</li>\r\n	<li>Blended and injection moulded slippers<br />\r\n	&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', 'uploads/66e7e08624ef3_vinyl.jpg', 7, 'Unicell: Foaming Agents', 'Unicell: Foaming Agents'),
(19, 'Zincosil:  Active Zinc Oxide', 'zincosil', '<p>MLA is India&rsquo;s Largest manufacturer of Active Zinc Oxide with plant Capacity 1000T/M. Zincosil is made by wet process unlike traditional French Process of Zinc Oxide. In this process all heavy metals such as Lead, Cadmium, Arsenic etc gets eliminate and keep it below 20PPM, with higher surface area 20-50 Sq Mtr/Gm. It provides numerous advantages for different applications. Zincosil is safe for human being, environment with ROHS Compliant and Sustainable product.</p>\r\n', 'uploads/678e541f8c520_zincosil.webp', '2024-05-29 12:30:08', '2025-05-20 15:04:37', 'Published', 'uploads/66f17158147df_zinc.jpg', '<h2>Applications</h2>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Rubber</li>\r\n	<li>Ceramics&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Cosmetics&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Petroleum&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Agriculture&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Animal Feed&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Paint Applications&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Pharmaceuticals&nbsp;<br />\r\n	&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', 'uploads/66f1715814956_zincapp.jpg', 4, 'Zincosi High Purity Zinc Oxide For Industrial Uses | MLA', 'Explore high-purity Zinc Oxide products with high activity & safety. Perfect for industrial, pharmaceutical, cosmetic, paint, & agricultural applications.'),
(20, 'Tulsi: Micronized Mineral Fillers / Extenders', 'tulsi', '<p>Snow-white china clay TULSI range we manufacture is very famous worldwide for its high whiteness, neutral pH, low moisture, free flowing nature, low loss on ignition and high chemical purity. We have Grit free grades for food applications, Surface Coated grades for increased dispersion , Carbonate free talc with whiteness as high as 97 % and free from grit, silica, quartz. We also have Bartyes, calcite and dolomite of different mesh size and colour . Our Minerals are not only finely grinded but are also micronized and levigated to remove coarse particles and make soft fine products.&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'uploads/66d1cdd24d988_tulsis.jfif', '2024-05-29 12:31:23', '2025-05-20 15:05:54', 'Published', 'uploads/66f174d5059df_white-powsder.webp', '<h2>Applications:</h2>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Widely used as a filler in rubber, footwear, paints, plastics, cosmetics, detergents, pharma, animal feed, chemicals, ceramics, pesticides etc.</li>\r\n	<li>Cables- used to increase insulation properties&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Paints-&nbsp;As a partial substitute of costly white pigment titanium dioxide.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', 'uploads/66f1728148095_tulsoapp.jpeg', 5, 'Tulsi Industrial Use Minerals Clay, Talc & More | MLA', 'MLA Group’s TULSI China Clay offers high whiteness, low moisture, and purity. Ideal for paints, rubber, plastics, ceramics, pharma, cables, and more.'),
(21, 'Unilub: Plastic Lubricants', 'unilub', '<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm\">UNILUB specializes in high-performance ester-based additives designed to enhance the production and performance of PVC and plastic products. Our additives offer superior lubrication, improved thermal stability, and enhanced processing efficiency, making them ideal for various applications within the plastic and polymer industries.</p>\r\n', 'uploads/67b733b513a6d_unilub-plastic-lubricants.webp', '2024-05-29 12:32:13', '2025-05-20 15:06:15', 'Published', 'uploads/66f17303399d0_meta.jpg', '<h2>Applications&nbsp;</h2>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>PVC Pipes / Fittings / Cables&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Masterbatches&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Cosmetics&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Pharmaceuticals&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>WPC, SPC&nbsp;<br />\r\n	&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', 'uploads/66f1730339b81_unilub.jpg', 6, 'High-Efficiency Additives for PVC, Cables & More | MLA', 'Enhance PVC & plastic performance with UNILUB ester-based additives. Boosts processing, thermal stability & efficiency in cables, WPC, cosmetics & more.\r\n\r\n'),
(22, 'Unisil: PPT Silica and Silicates', 'unisil', '<p>We have been in the silica business since 1975, where our R&amp;D has developed the world&#39;s highest absorption silica grade NK-7 with 500% absorption capacity. With an installed capacity of 1000 tons/month we are one of the largest manufacturers and have excellent spray dried silica as well with unmatched quality. We also have Hydrated calcium silicate with pH of 10 and very light material with absorption capacity of 350-400% and sodium aluminium silicate. Our silica ranges from ultra fine powder to granular/spray dried pellets.</p>\r\n', 'uploads/678e536c414ef_unisil-ppt-silica-and-silicates.webp', '2024-05-29 12:34:16', '2025-05-20 15:04:03', 'Published', 'uploads/66f175dc30471_silica.webp', '<h2>Applications:</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Few of the applications in silica include:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Cables and rubber products-&nbsp;&nbsp;As a reinforcing agent in&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Paints- As a matting and thickening agent</li>\r\n	<li>Food products- For anti caking and free flow in seasonings, spices, salts, cake mix, milk powder etc</li>\r\n	<li>Pesticides- Carrying agent for the liquid medicine</li>\r\n	<li>Detergents- for anti-caking and free flow</li>\r\n	<li>Toothpaste- as a thickening and polishing agent etc</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', 'uploads/66f170c58f182_silicapp.png', 3, 'Multi-Use Precipitated Silica Solutions | MLA Group', 'From cables to toothpaste, get multi-use unisil silica with high absorption. Available in fine powder, spray-dried, and granular forms for versatile applications.\r\n\r\n'),
(23, 'Unistab: PVC Heat Stabilizers', 'unistab', '<p>Stabilizers are chemical mixtures that are essential for the processing of PVCs and play a critical role in the development of the finished product to ensure the desired quality and durability. MLA Group portfolio of stabilizers, together with lubricants and other additives, offers tailored solutions for the performance requirements of finished products. With a vast experience in the field we implement best class in-house practices which drives our R&amp;D and ensure that our product our best in quality as well as consistency.&nbsp;We manufacture various types of PVC Heat Stabilizers :-&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Lead Based</li>\r\n	<li>Hybrid Low Lead Based</li>\r\n	<li>Calcium Zinc Based ( Non Toxic , Eco Friendly )</li>\r\n	<li>Mixed Metals ( Ba-Zn , Ba-Cd , Ba-Pb etc )</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', 'uploads/6750056062833_unistab-heat-stablizers.webp', '2024-05-29 12:34:45', '2025-05-20 14:57:20', 'Published', 'uploads/66f17715df56f_pvcflake.jpg', '<h2>Application :-</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">PVC (Polyvinyl Chloride) heat stabilizers are essential additives used in the production and processing of PVC materials. Their primary purpose is to prevent the degradation of PVC when exposed to high temperatures during manufacturing and throughout its service life. Here are some key applications of PVC heat stabilizers:</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">PVC Pipes &amp; Fittings</span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">PVC Profile</span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Wire &amp; Cables </span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Edgebands </span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">WPC </span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">SPC </span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', 'uploads/66f16b11ac6df_pvcapp-removebg-preview.png', 2, 'Chemical Stabilizers for Improved Material Stability', 'Get high-quality Unistab PVC heat stabilizers that boost thermal stability and durability in pipes, cables, profiles, WPC, SPC, and other composite applications.'),
(24, 'Pharma-Excipients', 'pharma-excipients', '<p>Our pharma division has in-house manufacturing of technicals, strong documentation support with all the requisite certificates, GMP certified plants, in-house AAS testing for maintaining negligible heavy metals in our products , and US-DMF registration for 20+ products. We also have an in house microbiology lab, to make the material free from these pathogens we put them in an ethylene oxide treatment chamber or we have to sterilize them by heat. We have products that conform to IP/BP/EP/USP/JP pharmacopoeias.</p>\r\n', 'uploads/67d81500d7d7f_pharma-excipients.webp', '2024-08-30 13:15:47', '2025-05-20 15:06:41', 'Published', 'uploads/66e0566b84d9d_tablet1.webp', '<h2>Applications:</h2>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Cosmetics</li>\r\n	<li>Food products</li>\r\n	<li>Tablet coating and filler in pharma products&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Zinc supplement and API for further reaction</li>\r\n	<li>32+ products for various other applications</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', 'uploads/66e0566b84f9e_cosmeticimg.jpg', 8, 'High-Quality Pharma Excipients Supplier | MLA Group\r\n\r\n', 'Get top-quality pharma excipients with GMP-grade safety—ideal for tablets, coatings, cosmetics, food products, zinc supplements & more. Clean & reliable.\r\n\r\n');
