(58, 'Precipitated Silica', 'silica', 'Leading Precipitated Silica Manufacturer & Supplier in India', 'MLA Group is a leading Indian manufacturers & suppliers of Precipitated Silica, we are one of the best exporter of Silica in the whole world at best price.', '<meta property=\"og:url\" content=\"https://www.mlagroup.com/silica.html\">\r\n<meta property=\"og:title\" content=\"Leading Precipitated Silica Manufacturer & Supplier in India\" />\r\n<meta property=\"og:description\" content=\"MLA Group is a leading Indian manufacturers & suppliers of Precipitated Silica, we are one of the best exporter of Silica in the whole world at best price.\" />\r\n<meta property=\"og:image\" content=\"https://www.mlagroup.com/admin/codes/product-image/silica_1.webp\" />\r\n<meta property=\"og:type\" content=\"website\">\r\n\r\n<meta name=\"twitter:url\" content=\"https://www.mlagroup.com/silica.html\">\r\n<meta name=\"twitter:title\" content=\"Leading Precipitated Silica Manufacturer & Supplier in India\">\r\n<meta name=\"twitter:image\" content=\"https://www.mlagroup.com/admin/codes/product-image/silica_1.webp\">\r\n<meta name=\"twitter:description\" content=\"MLA Group is a leading Indian manufacturers & suppliers of Precipitated Silica, we are one of the best exporter of Silica in the whole world at best price.\" />\r\n<meta name=\"twitter:creator\" content=\"MLA Group\">\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<script type=\"application/ld+json\">\r\n	{\r\n	  \"@context\": \"https://schema.org\",\r\n	  \"@type\": \"FAQPage\",\r\n	  \"mainEntity\": {\r\n		\"@type\": \"Question\",\r\n		\"name\": \"WHY SHOULD I PURCHASE PRECIPITATED SILICA FROM THE MLA GROUP?\",\r\n		\"acceptedAnswer\": {\r\n		  \"@type\": \"Answer\",\r\n		  \"text\": \"<p> At MLA Group, we fabricate items under a controlled climate and with high accuracy, severe quality controls, and standardized systems to present to you the best item each and every time. Because of our colossal limit and methodology, our costs are generally economical. We are the Leading Precipitated Silica manufacturers in India who are focused on constant improvement through R&D, to serve the clients with quality items at lower costs through higher usefulness and unparalleled client service.</p>\"\r\n		}\r\n	  }\r\n	}\r\n	</script>\r\n\r\n<script type=\"application/ld+json\">\r\n{\r\n  \"@context\": \"https://schema.org/\", \r\n  \"@type\": \"Product\", \r\n  \"name\": \"Precipitated Silica\",\r\n  \"image\": \"https://www.mlagroup.com/admin/codes/uploads/675004f0cbb1d_unisil-ppt-silica-and-silicates.webp\",\r\n  \"description\": \"Precipitation Silica is carried out in microprocessor controlled batch reaction vessels, used in different fields like pesticides, feedstuffs & food Items, chemicals, plastics & polymers, adhesives etc\",\r\n  \"brand\": {\r\n    \"@type\": \"Brand\",\r\n    \"name\": \"UNISIL\"\r\n  },\r\n  \"aggregateRating\": {\r\n    \"@type\": \"AggregateRating\",\r\n    \"ratingValue\": \"5\",\r\n    \"bestRating\": \"5\",\r\n    \"worstRating\": \"1\",\r\n    \"ratingCount\": \"1\"\r\n  }\r\n}\r\n</script>\r\n', 'product-image/silica_1.webp', NULL, '22', 'Unpublished', '<h2>Excellence Through Research &amp; Devlopment</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Synthetic Silica Products and Kanpur Chemical Industries, units of MLA Group of Industries are one of the largest manufacturers of precipitated silica / hydrated silica / amorphous silica / silicic acid and silicates today, having complete vertical integration, rigid quality control standards and unique product properties. Not only have we stood the competition against multinationals, but are the leaders in several fronts, where through intensive research we have developed products with unmatched properties, by standards. We cater to every segment of the market with user specific products. We started operations in 1985 and have today grown into a company with an annual production of 4000 MT/Annum and an expediture as high as 10% of net profits on R &amp; D annually.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>We are the leading manufacturer of precipitated calcium silicates in India and have promising quality over our products. We ensure multiple testing of our products through the experts and professionals which helped us to stand as leading precipitated silica suppliers/exporters in the world, following are some of ours unique properties:</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>A. Very High Water / Oil Absorption</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Upto 600% has been achieved and efforts are in progress to achieve the 800% mark. Most competing products have water-absorption upto 300% maximum only.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>B. Very Low Bulk Densities</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Upto 0.04 gm/cc has been achieved whereas competing products have 0.12 gm/cc minimum.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>C. Very High Surface Areas</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Upto 600 m2/gm has been achieved.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Production Facilities</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Precipitation is carried out in microprocessor controlled batch reaction vessels, followed by filler-presses/vaccum filters and flash/spray driers and finally micro-mill with classifier for micronization wherever required.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Pesticides</h3>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\" Pesticides\" src=\"https://mlagroup.com/admin/uploadck/pesticides.webp\" style=\"width: 143px; height: 150px;\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>&nbsp;For improvement in the suspension power and as a carrier for the active igredients, specially malathion, acephate and isoproton based formulations.</li>\r\n	<li>&nbsp;For improvement of free-flow characteristics and storage stability.</li>\r\n	<li>&nbsp;As a grinding auxillary.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h3>Feedstuffs &amp; Food Items</h3>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"Feedstuff And Food Items\" src=\"https://mlagroup.com/admin/uploadck/feedstuff-and-food-items.webp\" style=\"width: 140px; height: 150px;\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>&nbsp;Improvement in free-flow properties and storage stability of table salt, spices etc.</li>\r\n	<li>&nbsp;Anticaking of milk extenders and fat concentrates, feedstuff urea &amp; mineral mixtures.</li>\r\n	<li>&nbsp;Conversion of 75% acqueous choline chloride solution into stable 50% powder form.</li>\r\n	<li>&nbsp;Conversion of liquid active substances into powder form, e.g. ethoxyquin, flavours &amp; fragrances.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h3>Chemicals - Precipitated Silica</h3>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"Chemicals \" src=\"https://mlagroup.com/admin/uploadck/chemical.webp\" style=\"width: 150px; height: 96px;\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>&nbsp;Conversion of liquids to free flowing powder form (e.g. SP antioxidant &amp; other rubber chemicals).</li>\r\n	<li>&nbsp;As a grinding aid (e.g. with sulphur).</li>\r\n	<li>&nbsp;For anti-caking &amp; free flow. (e.g. Detergents).</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h3>Plastics &amp; Polymers - Precipitated Silica</h3>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"Plastic And Polymer\" src=\"https://mlagroup.com/admin/uploadck/plastic-and-polymer.webp\" style=\"width: 142px; height: 150px;\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>To provide reinforcement properties in PP, PVC, PE and Polystyrene based master batches.</li>\r\n	<li>As an anti-blocking agent in blown films &amp; foils.</li>\r\n	<li>Improvement in the mechanical characterstics of PVC flooring.</li>\r\n	<li>With Phenol + melamine resins for anti-caking during storage and improvement in dosing properties of molding compounds.</li>\r\n	<li>Auxillary during production of polychloroprene based adhesives.</li>\r\n	<li>With thermoplastic rubber for reduction in abrasion and increase in dimensional heat stability.</li>\r\n	<li>Reinforcement of Natural, SBR, Silicone, EVA, Nitrile, EPDM &amp; other rubbers.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h2>Other Products</h2>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Liquid Systems</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\nDue to high surface area they function as clarifying and adsorption agents (e.g.beverages).</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Adhesives</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\nTo adjust rheology and provide reinforcement.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Greases / Lubricants</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\nFor rheology control.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Paint, Dyes &amp; Printing inks</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\nAs a flatting / matting agent to reduce gloss or as a filler.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Paper Industry</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\nProvides lightness, whiteness &amp; improves mechanical properties.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Toothpaste &amp; Polishes</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\nAs a mild abrasive and for rheology control.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Pharmaceuticals</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\nAs a processing aid in tabletting &amp; pelletizing.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Cosmetics</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\nFor rheology control.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Unisil Precipitated Silica</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>UNISIL precipitated Silicas are available in various combinations of physical properties such primary and secondary particle size, surface area, bulk density, absorption capacity etc. It is available in three physical form Categories:-</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Powder Products</li>\r\n	<li>Spray Dried Granules</li>\r\n	<li>Compacted Pellets</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h2>FAQ&#39;s</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Why Should I Purchase Precipitated Silica From the Mla Group?</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>At MLA Group, we fabricate items under a controlled climate and with high accuracy, severe quality controls, and standardized systems to present to you the best item each and every time. Because of our colossal limit and methodology, our costs are generally economical. We are the Leading Precipitated Silica manufacturers in India who are focused on constant improvement through R&amp;D, to serve the clients with quality items at lower costs through higher usefulness and unparalleled client service.</p>\r\n', '<p bis_size=\"{&quot;x&quot;:20,&quot;y&quot;:20,&quot;w&quot;:1127,&quot;h&quot;:20,&quot;abs_x&quot;:306,&quot;abs_y&quot;:1072}\"><a bis_size=\"{&quot;x&quot;:20,&quot;y&quot;:23,&quot;w&quot;:133,&quot;h&quot;:14,&quot;abs_x&quot;:306,&quot;abs_y&quot;:1075}\"