ly listen to customer needs; carefully build product quality, sincerely provide services; and truly believe that serving the customers is the sole reason for our existence.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>The Product: Aluminium Stearate</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Aluminium Stearate is a white or slightly yellow powder, mainly used as a heat stabilizer and lubricant for PVC plastics, anti-settling agent and drier in the paint industry, waterproofing agent for fabrics, thickening agent for lubricating oil, etc. It is insoluble in water, ethanol, ether, but soluble in solvents such as alkali, turpentine, mineral oil, petroleum, kerosene, and benzene. It forms a thixotropic gel on heating with mineral oils and solvents which is the main premise of its use and design. We have hi-gel, supergel and non-gel grades. We manufacture all three types-&nbsp;<strong>aluminium mono-stearate, aluminium di-stearate and aluminium tri-stearate</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Special Features Of Our Aluminium Stearate</h2>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>&nbsp;Very high gelling power. Forms strong gel even at as low as 1.5-2.0% dosage</li>\r\n	<li>&nbsp;Moisture depletes gelling power. Our aluminium stearate has a very controlled moisture due to twin stage automatic drying system.</li>\r\n	<li>&nbsp;Manufactured in a dedicated plant, therefore, there are zero contaminants present, like zinc or calcium, which are gel breakers.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h2>Why Choose Us As Your Aluminium Stearate Suppliers?</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Since its establishment, MLA Group of Industries has always regarded product quality as the core of the company&#39;s participation in market competition. It is this successful positioning and our employees&#39; sound management and a strong awareness of the product quality that makes us professional&nbsp;<strong>Aluminium Stearate suppliers</strong>. We are a &quot;customer first&quot; company who strongly believe that our success depends on our product quality and the satisfaction of our customers. To this end, we work closely with every customer to support high-quality business services. The modern warehousing and advanced logistics system ensure the safety of chemicals and quick and timely delivery to customers. We are, thus, regarded as one of the most reputed&nbsp;<strong>Aluminium Stearate exporters in the World</strong>, with strong comprehensive strength in R&amp;D and marketing.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3 dir=\"ltr\">Our strengths include :</h3>\r\n\r\n<ul dir=\"ltr\">\r\n	<li>A) In house fabrication and erection</li>\r\n	<li>B) DSIR recognized in house R&amp;D equipped with laser particle size analyzer, BET surface area analyzer, etc</li>\r\n	<li>C) In house plastic laboratory equipped with a rheometer, VR testing, two roll, etc</li>\r\n	<li>D) The three-tier quality control system</li>\r\n	<li>E) Fast decision making due to the flat structure</li>\r\n	<li>F) Customer-driven &ndash; strong complaint handling system</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">At MLA Group, we promise reasonable prices, a short supply cy<strong>cle, and satisfactory after-sales service.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<h2 dir=\"ltr\">FAQS</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:null;\"><strong>What is the benefit of using Aluminium Stearate?</strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Aluminium Stearate is mainly used as gelling agent, used in the manufacturing of grease, oil drilling chemicals, explosives, water proofing of canvas in combination with paraffin wax and also as an anti-selling agent in paints. It also finds use as a gelling agent in pharmaceutical and cosmetic preparations for which we manufacture pharma grade product also. As a&nbsp;<strong>leading Aluminium Stearate exporters in India</strong>, we strictly control and manage all links related to product quality, establish scientific inspection standards, and ensure that the company maintains stable and qualified products.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:null;\"><strong>Where can I purchase premium quality aluminium stearate for industrial purposes?</strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>If you are looking for industrial-grade aluminum stearate, consider MLA Group as your&nbsp;<strong>Aluminium Stearate suppliers</strong>. In India, we are currently one of the&nbsp;<strong>leading Aluminium Stearate manufacturers</strong>. We continue to innovate around the needs and requirements of our customers and we believe in open cooperation with partners. We are committed to providing scientific research with competitive comprehensive solutions and services, continuously improving customer experience, and creating maximum value for customers.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:null;\"><strong>What type of aluminium stearate do you supply?</strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>As one of the<strong>&nbsp;Aluminium Stearate manufacturers in the World</strong>, at MLA Group, we provide fine quality Aluminium Stearate, available in different forms as per the needs of our customers. Our product, a white fine powder with moisture level less than 2 percent, is stored in fine conditions, out of human touch. We develop them using effective technology backed with strong scientific research. These chemicals are tested on several different quality standards and are inspected strictly in accordance with the procedures.</p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '', '<h2>Applications</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Our professionalism has promoted our rapid development and satisfied our domestic and foreign customers, making us a popular name among&nbsp;<strong>Aluminium Stearate suppliers</strong>&nbsp;not only in&nbsp;<strong>India</strong>&nbsp;but also&nbsp;<strong>in the world</strong>. We export premium quality metallic stearates to 46 countries, around every corner of the globe.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Uses of Aluminium Stearate include:</h2>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>&nbsp;Increasing viscosity in greases (especially graphite grease)</li>\r\n	<li>&nbsp;Form waterproof coating along with wax for canvas fabric coating (eg., boots, military tents, wtc.)</li>\r\n	<li>&nbsp;When heated