ible and rigid PVC applications.</p>\"  \r\n		}\r\n	  }]\r\n	}\r\n	</script>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<meta property=\"og:url\" content=\"https://www.mlagroup.com/calcium-zinc-stabilizer-manufacturers.html\">\r\n<meta property=\"og:title\" content=\"Leading Calcium zinc stabilizer manufacturers & suppliers\" />\r\n<meta property=\"og:description\" content=\"MLA Group is the leading manufacturing & supplying company of Calcium zinc stabilizer from the last 44 years. We are world-class exporter of zinc stabilizer.\" />\r\n<meta property=\"og:image\" content=\"https://www.mlagroup.com/admin/codes/product-image/calcium-zinc-stablizer.webp\" />\r\n<meta property=\"og:type\" content=\"website\">\r\n\r\n<meta name=\"twitter:url\" content=\"https://www.mlagroup.com/calcium-zinc-stabilizer-manufacturers.html\">\r\n<meta name=\"twitter:title\" content=\"Leading Calcium zinc stabilizer manufacturers & suppliers\">\r\n<meta name=\"twitter:image\" content=\"https://www.mlagroup.com/admin/codes/product-image/calcium-zinc-stablizer.webp\">\r\n<meta name=\"twitter:description\" content=\"MLA Group is the leading manufacturing & supplying company of Calcium zinc stabilizer from the last 44 years. We are world-class exporter of zinc stabilizer.\" />\r\n<meta name=\"twitter:creator\" content=\"MLA Group\">\r\n\r\n\r\n<script type=\"application/ld+json\">\r\n{\r\n  \"@context\": \"https://schema.org/\", \r\n  \"@type\": \"Product\", \r\n  \"name\": \"Calcium Zinc Stabilizer\",\r\n  \"image\": \"https://www.mlagroup.com/admin/codes/product-image/calcium-zinc-stablizer.webp\",\r\n  \"description\": \"Calcium zinc stabilizers are a complex mixture of over 10-15 ingredients like stearates, organic stabilizers, inorganic stabilizers, antioxidants, lubricants, fillers, etc. It is a non-toxic stabilizer that is the preferred choice over lead-based stabilizers which are completely banned in developed countries and slowly being phased out of the world.\",\r\n  \"brand\": {\r\n    \"@type\": \"Brand\",\r\n    \"name\": \"UniFlow\"\r\n  },\r\n  \"aggregateRating\": {\r\n    \"@type\": \"AggregateRating\",\r\n    \"ratingValue\": \"5\",\r\n    \"bestRating\": \"5\",\r\n    \"worstRating\": \"1\",\r\n    \"ratingCount\": \"1\"\r\n  }\r\n}\r\n</script>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n', 'product-image/calcium-zinc-stablizer_1.webp', NULL, '23', 'Unpublished', '<h2 bis_size=\"{\" x=\"\">Calcium zinc stabilizer suppliers in India</h2>\r\n\r\n<p bis_size=\"{\" x=\"\">MLA Group of Industries is one of the world&rsquo;s leading manufacturers and suppliers of Calcium zinc stabilizer, and a trending name in both national and international markets. As a global leader, we are committed to providing superior quality heat stabilizers that include lead-free&nbsp;<a bis_size=\"{\" x=\"\">PVC stabilizers</a>&nbsp;i.e., Calcium-Zinc based complex non-toxic stabilizers at competitive market prices. These stabilizers are ever evolving and with our in-house PVC lab and application centre, we carry out continuous research to improve existing products and develop new grades. With a production capacity of more than 1000 tons per month, we cater to a large segment of industries and have formed long term associations with many leading names in the industry.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3 bis_size=\"{\" x=\"\">The Product - Calcium Zinc Stabilizer</h3>\r\n\r\n<p bis_size=\"{\" x=\"\">Calcium zinc stabilizers are a complex mixture of over 10-15 ingredients like stearates, organic stabilizers, inorganic stabilizers, antioxidants, lubricants, fillers, etc. It is a non-toxic stabilizer that is the preferred choice over lead-based stabilizers which are completely banned in developed countries and slowly being phased out of the world.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2 bis_size=\"{\" x=\"\">Special Features of Our Calcium Zinc Stabilizer</h2>\r\n\r\n<p bis_size=\"{\" x=\"\">As the global leaders of today, and a well-known name among&nbsp;<strong bis_size=\"{\" x=\"\"><a bis_size=\"{\" x=\"\">Calcium Stearate</a>&nbsp;suppliers in the world&nbsp;</strong>, we are committed to developing high-quality calcium steerates that have the following unique properties:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul bis_size=\"{\" x=\"\">\r\n	<li bis_size=\"{\" x=\"\">&nbsp;High heat stability</li>\r\n	<li bis_size=\"{\" x=\"\">&nbsp;Processing fluidity and ease</li>\r\n	<li bis_size=\"{\" x=\"\">&nbsp;ILubricating ability</li>\r\n	<li bis_size=\"{\" x=\"\">&nbsp;Effective performance as per the need of the product ( customization )</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h2 bis_size=\"{\" x=\"\">Why Choose Us as Your Calcium Zinc Stabilizer Suppliers in India?</h2>\r\n\r\n<p bis_size=\"{\" x=\"\">At MLA Group Of Industries, we pride in our research &amp; development facilities that have helped us benchmark our products along the lines of international quality yet offering them at cost-effective prices to our customers, thereby, establishing ourselves as one of the&nbsp;<strong bis_size=\"{\" x=\"\">leading calcium zinc stabilizer manufacturers and suppliers in India.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p bis_size=\"{\" x=\"\">Not limited to geographical boundaries, we export to over 46 countries around every corner of the globe making us a leading name among Calcium zinc stabilizer exporters in India. With a huge investment in modern production, and stable quality and timely delivery, we are committed to becoming a model enterprise on a global scale.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3 bis_size=\"{\" x=\"\"><strong bis_size=\"{\" x=\"\">Our strengths lie in our</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<ul bis_size=\"{\" x=\"\">\r\n	<li bis_size=\"{\" x=\"\"><em bis_size=\"{\" x=\"\">A)</em>&nbsp;In house fabrication and erection</li>\r\n	<li bis_size=\"{\" x=\"\"><em bis_size=\"{\" x=\"\">B)&nbsp;</em>DSIR recognized in house R&amp;D equipped with laser particle size analyzer, BET surface area analyzer, etc</li>\r\n	<li bis_size=\"{\" x=\"\"><em bis_size=\"{\" x=\"\">C)&nbsp;</em>In house plastic laboratory equipped with a rheometer, VR testing, two rolls, etc</li>\r\n	<li bis_size=\"{\" x=\"\"><em bis_size=\"{\" x=\"\">D)</em>&nbsp;The three-tier quality control system</li>\r\n	<li bis_size=\"{\" x=\"\"><em bis_size=\"{\" x=\"\">E)&nbsp;</em>Fast decision making due to the flat structure</li>\r\n	<li bis_size=\"{\" x=\"\"><em bis_size=\"{\" x=\"\">F)&nbsp;</em>Customer-driven &ndash; strong complaint handling system</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h3 bis_size=\"{\" x=\"\">Technical Support</h3>\r\n\r\n<p bis_size=\"{\" x=\"\">At MLA Group Of Industries, we have in-house application labs with plastic and technology experts available for research and providing round the clock technical services to our clients. We can participate in your product development and production according to your needs, analyze the problems you encounter, and provide you with effective technical solutions.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2 bis_size=\"{\" x=\"\">FAQS</h2>\r\n\r\n<p bis_size=\"{\" x=\"\"><strong>What is the use of calcium zinc stabilizers?</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p bis_size=\"{\" x=\"\">The use of calcium zinc stabilizers has been common in PVC. They are widely used in many flexible and rigid PVC applications because of the characteristics of calcium zinc stabilized materials. Such stabilizing systems give products that have a high degree of clarity, good mechanical and electrical properties, excellent organoleptic properties, and good outdoor weather ability.</p>\r\n\r\n<p bis_size=\"{\" x=\"\"><strong>Where can I purchase industrial grade calcium zinc stabilizers?</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p bis_size=\"{\" x=\"\">MLA Group of industries is a leading name as<strong bis_size=\"{\" x=\"\">&nbsp;Calcium zinc stabilizer suppliers in India.</strong>&nbsp;We have amassed some reputable clients over a period of years who would vouch for our product quality and the economical prices. The company is now one of the leading exporters of calcium zinc stabilizers at the national &amp; international levels.</p>\r\n\r\n<p bis_size=\"{\" x=\"\"><strong>Are calcium zinc stabilizers safe to use?</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p bis_size=\"{\" x=\"\">Calcium zinc stabilizers are non-toxic&nbsp;<a bis_size=\"{\" x=\"\">PVC heat stabilizers</a>&nbsp;that pose no risks to human health or the environment. In fact, the use of calcium/zinc stabilizer systems has been common in PVC applications in the past few decades and are widely used in many flexible and rigid PVC applications.</p>\r\n\r\n<p bis_size=\"{\" x=\"\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '', '<h2>Applications</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>MLA Industries is a&nbsp;<strong>leading exporter</strong>&nbsp;of a wide range of&nbsp;<strong>Calcium Zinc Stabilizer&nbsp;</strong>extensively used for Pipes, Profiles, Cable, Footwear, etc, manufactured using only the finest materials conforming to stringent quality norms.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Our Calcium Zinc Stabilizer is used in :</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>In the cable industry or plasticized PVC ( 40-50 phr of plasticizers like DOP, DBP, TOTM, CPW, etc ) the grades are developed to give a good:</li>\r\n	<li>Static stability (color of PVC compound at 180C for different times, Tikki test, a chart of color deterioration with time is prepared )</li>\r\n	<li>Thermal stability ( congo-red time or time taken for the PVC compound to decompose )</li>\r\n	<li>Volume resistivity, the wet VR etc ( electrical properties ) Special grades for HVAC and HVDC cables</li>\r\n	<li>Color holding ( uncured compound should not change color with ageing ).</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>For this, we have a full-fledged PVC lab to check the performance of our various grades. The grades are defined on the basis of the service temperature of the cable and can be 70, 90, 105, or 125 degrees C. We accordingly have grades CZ-815, CZ-835, CZ-55, CZ-75, CZ-889, and many others as per the specific requirement of clients.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>In the pipe industry, which is unplasticized, hard, or rigid. The stabilizer is developed to give good stability and smooth flow through the extruder. This is done by static heat stability test, Rheometer test to check flow and stability properties, and through checking the load in actual extrusion on a pilot or full-scale plant. We have many grades including CZ-RP40 against Sunace 911 and CZ-321-P against more recent grade 3210 of Baerlocher. We also have economy grades like RP-20 for WPC and other applications like marble flooring.</p>\r\n', '2024-04-25 08:12:12', '2025-06-09 13:12:12'),
(64, 'Magnesium Stearate', 'magnesium-stearate-manufacturers', 'Leading Magnesium Stearate manufacturer & supplier in India', 'Buy Magnesium Stearate from the best manufacturers in India, we are the leading supplier & exporter of Stearate in the world, offering quality at affordability', '<script type=\"application/ld+json\">\r\n{\r\n  \"@context\": \"https://schema.org\",\r\n  \"@type\": \"FAQPage\",\r\n  \"mainEntity\": [{\r\n    \"@type\": \"Question\",\r\n    \"name\": \"What is the USP of MLA Magnesium stearate?\",\r\n    \"acceptedAnswer\": {\r\n      \"@type\": \"Answer\",\r\n      \"text\": \"MLA Group of Industries is a prominent name among Magnesium Stearate manufacturers in India. Operating for over 45 years in the production, supply, and export of chemicals, we hold immense industry experience in manufacturing all kinds of metallic stearates including Magnesium Stearate.\"\r\n    }\r\n  },{\r\n    \"@type\": \"Question\",\r\n    \"name\": \"Why should I choose MLA Group as my Magnesium Stearate suppliers?\",\r\n    \"acceptedAnswer\": {\r\n      \"@type\": \"Answer\",\r\n      \"text\": \"MLA Group of Industries is a leading name engaged in manufacturing and supplying the finest range of Magnesium Stearate. All our products pass through several quality checks at all stages and are deemed fit for dispatch only after thorough consideration of industry laid parameters. We also provide after-sales service and have a strong product recall policy in case of defective products.\"\r\n    }\r\n  },{\r\n    \"@type\": \"Question\",\r\n    \"name\": \"How should magnesium stearate be stored?\",\r\n    \"acceptedAnswer\": {\r\n      \"@type\": \"Answer\",\r\n      \"text\": \"It is recommended to store the magnesium stearate in a dry, ventilated area. You should also avoid direct sunlight and high temperatures. You can store in a closed container; in a cool, dry, well-ventilated area, away from strong oxidizing agents.\"\r\n    }\r\n  }]\r\n}\r\n</script>\r\n\r\n\r\n<meta property=\"og:title\" content=\"Leading Magnesium Stearate manufacturer & supplier in India\" />\r\n<meta property=\"og:description\" content=\"Buy Magnesium Stearate from the best manufacturers in India, we are the leading supplier & exporter of Stearate in the world, offering quality at affordability\" />\r\n<meta property=\"og:image\" content=\"https://www.mlagroup.com/admin/codes/product-image/magenisium-sterate.webp\" />\r\n<meta property=\"og:url\" content=\"https://www.mlagroup.com/magnesium-stearate-manufacturers.html\" />\r\n<meta property=\"og:logo\" content=\"https://www.mlagroup.com/images/logo-MLA.png\" />\r\n<meta property=\"og:type\" content=\"website\" />\r\n\r\n\r\n<meta name=\"twitter:url\" content=\"https://www.mlagroup.com/magnesium-stearate-manufacturers.html\">\r\n<meta name=\"twitter:title\" content=\"Leading Magnesium Stearate manufacturer & supplier in India\">\r\n<meta name=\"twitter:image\" content=\"https://www.mlagroup.com/admin/codes/product-image/magenisium-sterate.webp\">\r\n<meta name=\"twitter:description\" content=\"Buy Magnesium Stearate from the best manufacturers in India, we are the leading supplier & exporter of Stearate in the world, offering quality at affordability\" />\r\n<meta name=\"twitter:creator\" content=\"MLA Group\">\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n', 'product-image/magenisium-sterate_1.webp', NULL, '17', 'Unpublished', '<h2>Magnesium Stearate Exporter in India</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>MLA Group of Industries is a prominent name among Magnesium Stearate manufacturers in India. Operating for over 45 years in the production, supply, and export of chemicals, we hold immense industry experience in manufacturing all kinds of metallic stearates including Magnesium Stearate.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>With a massive production capacity of 800 tons per month, we are today a Leading Magnesium Stearate supplier not only in India but also in the world. Our company has strong production technology, advanced scientific research, and a perfect quality management system, and its products have been sold to all provinces and cities across the country and worldwide. It is because of our diligent customer service and fair market prices that our company occupies one of the leading positions among competitors in the sales of magnesium stearate. We export to 45 countries and are a STAR EXPORT HOUSE certified by the Indian government.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>We specialize in the production of&nbsp;<strong>pharma grade Magnesium Stearate&nbsp;</strong>with materials conforming to IP / BP/ USP / EP / JP / NF.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>The Product - Magnesium Stearate</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Magnesium Stearate is a magnesium salt of stearic acid. It is an additive widely used by the pharmacological area because it provides various functionalities to the formulations since it has lubricating, water-repellent, anti-flake, and release properties which attribute it to the products that are made with it. It is also used in plastics as a lubricant.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Magnesium Stearate Properties</h2>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>It is a light white powder with a fine appearance.</li>\r\n	<li>It feels smooth and greasy.</li>\r\n	<li>It is insoluble in water, ethanol, and ether.</li>\r\n	<li>It is soluble in hot water and hot ethanol.</li>\r\n	<li>It decomposes into stearic acid and the corresponding magnesium salt when acidic.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h2>Why Choose Us as Your Magnesium Stearate Suppliers In India ?</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>We are favored by customers for our excellent product quality, good company reputation, and perfect after-sales service. We have developed rapidly under the guidance of the rigorous, pragmatic, efficient, and lean development concept introduced advanced technology and equipment, and have a complete set of equipment production lines, which has laid a solid foundation for the company&#39;s sustainable development. We work with a group of diligent professionals, who are well-trained and experienced in the realm of producing superior quality Magnesium Stearate. With the production and management philosophy of &quot;customize and specialize&quot; and &quot;beginning with customer needs and ending with customer satisfaction&quot;, our company has won praise from users and has become one of the leading magnesium stearate suppliers in the world.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Our Approach</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>At MLA Group, we always adhere to the business philosophy of &ldquo;quality first, integrity first,&rdquo; through continuous innovation and progress. We are constantly applying new technologies and new processes, actively developing new products, reducing costs, and improving quality. It is the purpose of our company to provide all customers with timely, complete, and high-quality sales services.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Certifications</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Our manufacturing facility is</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>ISO 9001: 2015 certified</li>\r\n	<li>GMP Certified</li>\r\n	<li>FDA approved ( FSSAI certified )</li>\r\n	<li>HALAL certified</li>\r\n	<li>Kosher certified</li>\r\n	<li>Drug controller certified ( Pharma Division )</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Contact us now for more information and we will be happy to assist you.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>FAQS</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>What is the USP of MLA Magnesium stearate?</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>MLA stearates are unique because of not only the stringent process control but also the plant being of totally SS 316 L construction, leading to a very pure product. The product has low free fatty acid, very fine particle size, and is free from contamination as it passed through air classifier as well as mechanical sieving in the final stage of production. There are tailor-made grades as per the application and specifications of the customer.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Why should I choose MLA Group as my Magnesium Stearate suppliers?</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>MLA Group of Industries is a leading name engaged in manufacturing and supplying the finest range of Magnesium Stearate. All our products pass through several quality checks at all stages and are deemed fit for dispatch only after thorough consideration of industry laid parameters. We also provide after-sales service and have a strong product recall policy in case of the defective products.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>How should magnesium stearate be stored?</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>It is recommended to store the magnesium stearate in a dry, ventilated area. You should also avoid direct sunlight and high temperatures. You can store in a closed container; in a cool, dry, well-ventilated area, away from strong oxidizing agents.</p>\r\n', '', '<h2>Applications</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>We are a leading Magnesium Stearate supplier and exporters of Magnesium Stearate that is widely used in :</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Food, medicine, paint, plastics, rubber, textiles, and other industries, mainly as an emulsifier, mold release agent, lubricant, stabilizer, accelerator, cosmetic base material, etc.</li>\r\n	<li>This substance partially replaces the white matt pigment, which also makes it possible to use it in cosmetology. In creams, it acts as a lubricant and significantly increases glide.</li>\r\n	<li>Magnesium stearate is also used as an active stabilizer in PVC production.</li>\r\n	<li>In addition, the substance is used as a supplement in the manufacture of pharmaceuticals.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '2024-04-25 08:15:49', '2025-06-09 13:13:09'),
(65, 'Pharma Excipients', 'pharma-excipients-manufacturers', 'Leading Pharma Excipients manufacturer & supplier in India', 'We are the leading manufacturer & supplier of Pharma Excipients in India, offering our services from last 44 years we export in over 43 countries at best price.', '<script type=\"application/ld+json\"> 	{ 	  \"@context\": \"https://schema.org\", 	  \"@type\": \"FAQPage\", 	  \"mainEntity\": [{ 		\"@type\": \"Question\", 		\"name\": \"What advantage do I get if I buy from MLA?\", 		\"acceptedAnswer\": { 		  \"@type\": \"Answer\", 		  \"text\": \"<p>MLA is the bulk producer of most of the excipients that it\'s pharma division is selling in its group units. Hence we get the advantage of economies of scale and pass it on to our customers. Being a bulk manufacturer our mindset is inclined to volumes and not towards high profits. The Pharma Division works independently with the highest possible standards to ensure near zero failure and risk. We have the capability to develop product as per the customer\'s formulation need by modifying particular properties to their need.</p> \" 		} 	  },{ 		\"@type\": \"Question\", 		\"name\": \" Which Pharmacopeia does MLA Group follow?  \", 		\"acceptedAnswer\": { 		  \"@type\": \"Answer\", 		  \"text\": \"<p>We manufacture products as per the following</p> 	<ul>		            		 	<li>Indian Pharmacopeia - IP</li> 	<li> British Pharmacopeia - BP</li> 	<li>US Pharmacopeia - USP </li> 	<li>European Pharmacopeia - EP</li> 	<li>Japanese Pharmacopeia - JP</li> 	</ul> 	<p>Apart from this multi-compendia grades are also available which meet all of the above monographs for a particular substance.</p> \"  		   } 	  },{ 		\"@type\": \"Question\", 		\"name\": \"How can I get the documents required for statutory approvals in my company?  \", 		\"acceptedAnswer\": { 		  \"@type\": \"Answer\", 		  \"text\": \"<p>MLA provides Technical Data Pack ( TDP ) to its customers containing all certifications, declarations, COA, TDS, MOA, stability data etc for each substance in a single file. Hence the workload of customer to compile and assimilate information at one place is reduced. Apart from this the Site Master File ( SMF ), Drug Master file ( DMF ) -open part are available for customers.  </p>\"  			} 	  },{ 		\"@type\": \"Question\", 		\"name\": \"Is MLA open for customer audit?  \", 		\"acceptedAnswer\": { 		  \"@type\": \"Answer\", 		  \"text\": \"<p>Yes, we welcome our customers to audit us as it is a very important step to building trust between the organizations. It also helps us to learn from our customers and improve our processes. We can support both physical and virtual ( on-line audit ).</p>\"  		} 	  }] 	} 	</script>\r\n\r\n\r\n<meta property=\"og:title\" content=\"Leading Pharma Excipients manufacturer & supplier in India\" />\r\n<meta property=\"og:description\" content=\"We are the leading manufacturer & supplier of Pharma Excipients in India, offering our services from last 44 years we export in over 43 countries at best price.\" />\r\n<meta property=\"og:image\" content=\"https://www.mlagroup.com/admin/codes/uploads/pharma-excipients.webp\" />\r\n<meta property=\"og:url\" content=\"https://www.mlagroup.com/pharma-excipients-manufacturers.html\" />\r\n<meta property=\"og:logo\" content=\"https://www.mlagroup.com/images/logo-MLA.png\" />\r\n<meta property=\"og:type\" content=\"website\" />\r\n\r\n\r\n<meta name=\"twitter:url\" content=\"https://www.mlagroup.com/pharma-excipients-manufacturers.html\">\r\n<meta name=\"twitter:title\" content=\"Leading Pharma Excipients manufacturer & supplier in India\">\r\n<meta name=\"twitter:image\" content=\"https://www.mlagroup.com/admin/codes/product-image/magenisium-sterate.webp\">\r\n<meta name=\"twitter:description\" content=\"We are the leading manufacturer & supplier of Pharma Excipients in India, offering our services from last 44 years we export in over 43 countries at best price.\" />\r\n<meta name=\"twitter:creator\" content=\"MLA Group\">\r\n', 'product-image/pharmaceutical-excipients_1_2_3_4_5_6_7_8_9_10_11_12_13_14_15_16_17_18_19_20_21_22_23_24_25.webp', NULL, '24', 'Unpublished', '<h2>Leading Pharma Excipients exporters in India</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>MLA Group of Industries is a&nbsp;<strong>leading Pharma Excipients manufacturers in India</strong>&nbsp;that produces and supplies specialty chemicals and excipients to the pharmaceutical industry. We have independent R&amp;D and production capabilities where pharma raw material manufacturing is done under very closely controlled conditions, both in terms of infrastructure ( i.e., building, machinery, etc ) as well as process ( manpower, records, testing, etc ). We have permission for IP/ BP/USP/JP/EP from the Food and Drug Administration. Our constant search for new processes and certifications worldwide provides us with the necessary tools to be able to offer you products with the highest and most updated quality standards as well as most affordable prices.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>One of the&nbsp;<strong>leading Pharma Excipients exporters in India</strong>, we focus on more than just manufacturing and supplying raw materials. We specialize in the development of products that guarantee the best quality and add value. We get involved with our customers in their manufacturing process where needed; provide them with advice, technical services, and logistics and other support, making this process smoother and more efficient.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>The Product - Pharma Excipients</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Excipients are useful in the manufacturing process, to aid in the handling of the active substance concerned, such as by facilitating powder flowability or non-stick properties, in addition to aiding in vitro stability such as prevention of denaturation or aggregation over the expected shelf life.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Our commendable range of Pharma excipients includes high functionality excipients, binders, disintegrants, lubricants, functional fillers, thickeners, stabilizers, carriers, and coatings. As a&nbsp;<strong>Leading Pharma Excipients suppliers in India</strong>, all our formulations are done in accordance with the set FDA norms and guidelines. Our products are free of all heavy metals, pathogens and impurities, being manufactured in a GMP certified plant following stringent failure, mode, effect analysis.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Our Advantages:</h2>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Pharma Excipients manufacturing is done under very closely controlled conditions, both in terms of infrastructure ( building, machinery, etc ) as well as process ( manpower, records, testing, etc ). The plant in run as per the guidelines in Schedule M.</li>\r\n	<li>&nbsp;We have a stability chamber having adjustable heat and humidity that is used to check the product stability. This provides our customers with data of change in material&#39;s critical properties over a period of 2-3 years if they so require. We also have in house AAS, PSD analyzer, Surface area analyzer.</li>\r\n	<li>&nbsp;Pharma raw materials are different from normal because they are going to be used for human consumption. Therefore, to guarantee maximum purity, we have our in-house microbiology lab to make sure that our products are free of all pathogens and heavy metals.</li>\r\n	<li>A company making IP( pharma ) grade products is supposed to ensure that the products it manufactures finally meet the specifications laid down. At MLA Group, we have permission for IP/ BP/USP/EP/JP from the drug controller office or Food and Drug Administration.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h2>Product Range:</h2>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<thead>\r\n	</thead>\r\n	<thead>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th>S.No</th>\r\n			<th>Product Name</th>\r\n			<th>Specification</th>\r\n			<th>Use</th>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</thead>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>1</td>\r\n			<td>Magnesium Stearate</td>\r\n			<td>IP/BP/USP/EP/JP</td>\r\n			<td>Excipients</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>2</td>\r\n			<td>Calcium Stearate</td>\r\n			<td>IP/BP/USP/EP/JP</td>\r\n			<td>Excipient