<td>Synthetic Aluminum Silicate</td>\r\n			<td>JP</td>\r\n			<td>Excipients</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>18</td>\r\n			<td>Natural Aluminum Silicate</td>\r\n			<td>JP</td>\r\n			<td>Excipients</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td rowspan=\"3\">19</td>\r\n			<td>Starch</td>\r\n			<td>IP</td>\r\n			<td>Excipients</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Starch (Corn)</td>\r\n			<td>USP/JP</td>\r\n			<td>Excipients</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Starch(Maize)</td>\r\n			<td>BP</td>\r\n			<td>Excipients</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>20</td>\r\n			<td>Bentonite</td>\r\n			<td>USP/JP</td>\r\n			<td>Excipients</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>21</td>\r\n			<td>Barium Sulphate</td>\r\n			<td>BP/USP/EP/JP</td>\r\n			<td>Excipients</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>22</td>\r\n			<td>Purified Siliceous Earth</td>\r\n			<td>USP</td>\r\n			<td>Excipients</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>23</td>\r\n			<td>Stearic Acid</td>\r\n			<td>USP/BP</td>\r\n			<td>Excipients</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n\r\n<h2>Why Choose Us as Your Pharma Excipients Suppliers in India?</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>MLA Group of Industries is a prominent name among&nbsp;<strong>leading Pharma Excipients exporters in the World</strong>, backed with 45 years of extensive experience in the manufacture, purification, import, export and distribution of Chemical Products. We have established commercial relationships in more than 46 countries around every corner of the globe. Our main objective is to offer quality products and services that provide confidence and security to our customers, in addition to fully and satisfactorily meeting their expectations and needs.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>As one of the&nbsp;<strong>leading Pharma Excipients manufacturers in the World</strong>, we have stringent norms on quality assurance with strict recall guidelines in case of any lapse. We have two manufacturing chemists and two analytical chemists and a microbiologist in our team.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>FAQS</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>What Advantage Do I Get if I Buy From Mla?</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>MLA is the bulk producer of most of the excipients that it&#39;s pharma division is selling in its group units. Hence we get the advantage of economies of scale and pass it on to our customers. Being a bulk manufacturer our mindset is inclined to volumes and not towards high profits. The Pharma Division works independently with the highest possible standards to ensure near zero failure and risk. We have the capability to develop product as per the customer&#39;s formulation need by modifying particular properties to their need.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Which Pharmacopeia Does Mla Group Follow?</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>We manufacture products as per the following</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Indian Pharmacopeia - IP</li>\r\n	<li>British Pharmacopeia - BP</li>\r\n	<li>US Pharmacopeia - USP</li>\r\n	<li>European Pharmacopeia - EP</li>\r\n	<li>Japanese Pharmacopeia - JP</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Apart from this multi-compendia grades are also available which meet all of the above monographs for a particular substance.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:null;\"><strong>How Can I Get the Documents Required for Statutory Approvals in My Company?</strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>MLA provides Technical Data Pack ( TDP ) to its customers containing all certifications, declarations, COA, TDS, MOA, stability data etc for each substance in a single file. Hence the workload of customer to compile and assimilate information at one place is reduced. Apart from this the Site Master File ( SMF ), Drug Master file ( DMF ) -open part are available for customers.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:null;\"><strong>Is Mla Open for Customer Audit?</strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Yes, we welcome our customers to audit us as it is a very important step to building trust between the organizations. It also helps us to learn from our customers and improve our processes. We can support both physical and virtual ( on-line audit ).</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Being, one of the leading Pharma Excipients exporters in India, we always have been a preferred supplier for Pharma Excipient. We are currently serving more than 43 countries around every corner of the globe. Our constant growth is making us a Leading Pharma Excipients supplier and manufactures in India &amp; in the world At MLA Group, we make items under a controlled climate and with high exactness. Because of our gigantic limit and forceful methodology, our costs are generally practical. We are a main leading Pharma Excipients manufacturers in India who is focused on the quality of our products.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>All specifications given here are only indicative, there are several application specific grades under each category, please write to us for exact specifications.</p>\r\n', '', '<h3>Applications</h3>\r\n', '2024-04-25 08:20:40', '2025-06-09 13:15:53');
