quot;abs_x&quot;:306,&quot;abs_y&quot;:1625}\">Calcium Hydroxide Pharma Grade</h2>\r\n\r\n<p bis_size=\"{&quot;x&quot;:20,&quot;y&quot;:59,&quot;w&quot;:1127,&quot;h&quot;:62,&quot;abs_x&quot;:306,&quot;abs_y&quot;:1664}\">MLA Group of industries is a leading calcium hydroxide pharma-grade manufacturer in India, known for providing application-specific grades with extremely good quality at honest market prices. We make UNISIL ranges of calcium hydroxide by crushing the raw material to form fragments. Our inventive method is carried out with the aim of increasing enterprise profit, product processing technique, and enhancing the core competitiveness of the enterprise.</p>\r\n\r\n<p bis_size=\"{&quot;x&quot;:20,&quot;y&quot;:134,&quot;w&quot;:1127,&quot;h&quot;:62,&quot;abs_x&quot;:306,&quot;abs_y&quot;:1739}\">The complete manufacturing process is carried out in a Drug Controller authorized India FDA approved facility located in Kanpur. We own AHU with HEPA filters for a controlled, limited, and sterilized manufacturing procedure. We also own an in-house microbiology lab. We are also audited and certified with state GMP, a great designation that very few manufacturers in our field hold. Our manufactured products conform to IP/ BP/USP/ JP / EP/ NF monographs. The site master file is available.</p>\r\n\r\n<p bis_size=\"{&quot;x&quot;:20,&quot;y&quot;:210,&quot;w&quot;:1127,&quot;h&quot;:41,&quot;abs_x&quot;:306,&quot;abs_y&quot;:1815}\">Our enterprise integrates R&amp;D, production, and sales, supported by a team of experts, all of whom are qualified engineers in this field. Our motto is to make betterment in our production equipment and production technology by maintaining our position as one of the top calcium hydroxide pharma-grade suppliers and exporters in the world.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2 bis_size=\"{&quot;x&quot;:20,&quot;y&quot;:267,&quot;w&quot;:1127,&quot;h&quot;:18,&quot;abs_x&quot;:306,&quot;abs_y&quot;:1872}\">The Product - Calcium Hydroxide Pharma Grade</h2>\r\n\r\n<p bis_size=\"{&quot;x&quot;:20,&quot;y&quot;:300,&quot;w&quot;:1127,&quot;h&quot;:83,&quot;abs_x&quot;:306,&quot;abs_y&quot;:1905}\">Calcium hydroxide, traditionally being called hydrated lime or slaked lime, is an inorganic compound whose chemical formula is Ca(OH)2. It is a free-flowing white powder, fine in nature, free from grits &amp; other contaminations, and is produced when calcium oxide (quicklime) is &quot;slaked&quot; with water to form &quot;Hydrated Lime&quot;. We provide supreme quality optical products, compliant to various guidebooks, being ardently processed under good manufacturing processes. The generated chemical is used in various industries like food chemical, cosmetic, water treatment, pharmaceutical, and many more. The general lifespan of the product is three to six months from the date of manufacturing.</p>\r\n\r\n<p bis_size=\"{&quot;x&quot;:20,&quot;y&quot;:396,&quot;w&quot;:1127,&quot;h&quot;:62,&quot;abs_x&quot;:306,&quot;abs_y&quot;:2001}\">We feel proud of ourselves for being an affluent manufacturer, supplier and exporter of a high-quality calcium hydroxide pharma-grade range. The complete process is carried out under the proper guidance of our specialized researchers in accordance with the market guidelines. Our products are absolved from all known allergens and do not contain any prohibitory or toxic chemicals or non-kosher components. Furthermore, our calcium hydroxide pharma grade is also available in various packaging options to our esteemed customers.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2 bis_size=\"{&quot;x&quot;:20,&quot;y&quot;:475,&quot;w&quot;:1127,&quot;h&quot;:23,&quot;abs_x&quot;:306,&quot;abs_y&quot;:2080}\">General Properties of Calcium Hydroxide</h2>\r\n\r\n<ul bis_size=\"{&quot;x&quot;:20,&quot;y&quot;:514,&quot;w&quot;:1127,&quot;h&quot;:145,&quot;abs_x&quot;:306,&quot;abs_y&quot;:2119}\">\r\n	<li bis_size=\"{&quot;x&quot;:60,&quot;y&quot;:514,&quot;w&quot;:1047,&quot;h&quot;:20,&quot;abs_x&quot;:346,&quot;abs_y&quot;:2119}\">The molar molar mass is 74.09 g/mol</li>\r\n	<li bis_size=\"{&quot;x&quot;:60,&quot;y&quot;:535,&quot;w&quot;:1047,&quot;h&quot;:20,&quot;abs_x&quot;:346,&quot;abs_y&quot;:2140}\">It appears as colorless crystals or white powder in nature</li>\r\n	<li bis_size=\"{&quot;x&quot;:60,&quot;y&quot;:556,&quot;w&quot;:1047,&quot;h&quot;:20,&quot;abs_x&quot;:346,&quot;abs_y&quot;:2161}\">It is odorless</li>\r\n	<li bis_size=\"{&quot;x&quot;:60,&quot;y&quot;:577,&quot;w&quot;:1047,&quot;h&quot;:20,&quot;abs_x&quot;:346,&quot;abs_y&quot;:2182}\">Its melting point is 580&acirc;&bdquo;&fnof;</li>\r\n	<li bis_size=\"{&quot;x&quot;:60,&quot;y&quot;:598,&quot;w&quot;:1047,&quot;h&quot;:20,&quot;abs_x&quot;:346,&quot;abs_y&quot;:2203}\">It is soluble in water, acids, and glycerol</li>\r\n	<li bis_size=\"{&quot;x&quot;:60,&quot;y&quot;:618,&quot;w&quot;:1047,&quot;h&quot;:20,&quot;abs_x&quot;:346,&quot;abs_y&quot;:2223}\">It is insoluble in alcohol</li>\r\n	<li bis_size=\"{&quot;x&quot;:60,&quot;y&quot;:639,&quot;w&quot;:1047,&quot;h&quot;:20,&quot;abs_x&quot;:346,&quot;abs_y&quot;:2244}\">It is basic or alkaline in nature</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><meta charset=\"utf-8\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<h2 dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\"><b id=\"docs-internal-guid-5c6abe8f-7fff-7003-5d36-720fbdc0ebf2\">Why choose us as your Calcium Hydroxide Pharma Grade Suppliers?</b></h2>\r\n\r\n<p bis_size=\"{&quot;x&quot;:20,&quot;y&quot;:716,&quot;w&quot;:1127,&quot;h&quot;:62,&quot;abs_x&quot;:306,&quot;abs_y&quot;:2321}\">The <a bis_size=\"{&quot;x&quot;:46,&quot;y&quot;:719,&quot;w&quot;:65,&quot;h&quot;:14,&quot;abs_x&quot;:332,&quot;abs_y&quot;:2324}\" href=\"https://www.mlagroup.com/\"><span style=\"color:#3498db;\">MLA Group</span></a> of industries has grown rapidly over the years. We believe in maintaining our commitment to research and development (R&amp;D) of new medicines and treatments that save lives, increase life spans, reduce suffering, prevent surgeries, and shorten hospital stays. We deliver products