1011,&quot;w&quot;:1127,&quot;h&quot;:41,&quot;abs_x&quot;:306,&quot;abs_y&quot;:2616}\">With the help of pH paper, you can check the quality of calcium hydroxide. First, dip the strip of the pH paper into the calcium hydroxide solution and then take it out. There will be a change in pH paper. Now, compare the color of the paper with the pH scale to identify the pH of the solution. A pH value between 10 to 11 is indicative of good quality calcium hydroxide.</p>\r\n\r\n<p bis_size=\"{&quot;x&quot;:20,&quot;y&quot;:1065,&quot;w&quot;:1127,&quot;h&quot;:20,&quot;abs_x&quot;:306,&quot;abs_y&quot;:2670}\"><strong bis_size=\"{&quot;x&quot;:20,&quot;y&quot;:1069,&quot;w&quot;:299,&quot;h&quot;:14,&quot;abs_x&quot;:306,&quot;abs_y&quot;:2674}\">What are the applications of calcium hydroxide?</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p bis_size=\"{&quot;x&quot;:20,&quot;y&quot;:1099,&quot;w&quot;:1127,&quot;h&quot;:20,&quot;abs_x&quot;:306,&quot;abs_y&quot;:2704}\">Calcium hydroxide has a wide area of usage like - industrial area, environmental usage, health-related, chemical industries, and other lime usages.</p>\r\n', '', '<h2>General Applications of Calcium Hydroxide&nbsp;</h2>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Water softening</li>\r\n	<li>Neutralisation of pickling&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Manufacturing of insecticides and pesticides</li>\r\n	<li>In various chemical processes for pH control</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '2024-04-25 13:43:39', '2025-10-24 11:47:03');
