(84, 'Sorbitan Monostearate', 'sorbitan-monostearate-manufacturers-in-india', 'Leading Sorbitan Monosearate Manufacturers in India', 'MLA Group is a leading manufacturer & supplier of Sorbitan Monosearate, we are one of the best exporters of SMS in the world offering the best price.', '<script type=\"application/ld+json\">\r\n{\r\n  \"@context\": \"https://schema.org\",\r\n  \"@type\": \"FAQPage\",\r\n  \"mainEntity\": [{\r\n    \"@type\": \"Question\",\r\n    \"name\": \"Is the Sorbitan Monostearate manufactured by you Halal?\",\r\n    \"acceptedAnswer\": {\r\n      \"@type\": \"Answer\",\r\n      \"text\": \"Yes, as the leading Sorbitan Monostearate manufacturers and exporters in the world, we provide a synthetic ester that would be halal complying with the Muslim policy as the fatty acid stearic acid is derived from vegetable oils instead of animal origins.\"\r\n    }\r\n  },{\r\n    \"@type\": \"Question\",\r\n    \"name\": \"Is Sorbitan Monostearate manufactured by you Vegan?\",\r\n    \"acceptedAnswer\": {\r\n      \"@type\": \"Answer\",\r\n      \"text\": \"Yes, it is vegan as the raw material stearic acid is derived from vegetable oils and the manufacturing process is without the use of animal matter or products derived from animal origin.\"\r\n    }\r\n  },{\r\n    \"@type\": \"Question\",\r\n    \"name\": \"What is the shelf life of Sorbitan Monostearate manufactured by you? Also, what is the legal status on the same?\",\r\n    \"acceptedAnswer\": {\r\n      \"@type\": \"Answer\",\r\n      \"text\": \"Shelf Life: Sorbitan Monostearate manufactured at MLA Group has a shelf life of one year from the date of production, if stored under mentioned storage conditions and unopened packaging.\r\nLegal Status:Our SMS meets the specifications fixed by FAO/WHO and the EU. However, users must check for permissibility for the use of this product in foods in their own country as the food laws may differ in each country.\"\r\n    }\r\n  }]\r\n}\r\n</script>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<meta property=\"og:title\" content=\"Leading Sorbitan Monosearate Manufacturers in India\" />\r\n<meta property=\"og:description\" content=\"MLA Group is a leading manufacturer & supplier of Sorbitan Monosearate, we are one of the best exporters of SMS in the world offering the best price.\" />\r\n<meta property=\"og:image\" content=\"https://www.mlagroup.com/admin/codes/product-image/sorbitan-monostearate.webp\" />\r\n<meta property=\"og:url\" content=\"https://www.mlagroup.com/sorbitan-monostearate-manufacturers-in-india.html\" />\r\n<meta property=\"og:logo\" content=\"https://www.mlagroup.com/images/logo-MLA.png\" />\r\n<meta property=\"og:type\" content=\"website\" />\r\n\r\n\r\n<meta name=\"twitter:url\" content=\"https://www.mlagroup.com/sorbitan-monostearate-manufacturers-in-india.html\">\r\n<meta name=\"twitter:title\" content=\"Leading Sorbitan Monosearate Manufacturers in India\">\r\n<meta name=\"twitter:image\" content=\"https://www.mlagroup.com/admin/codes/product-image/sorbitan-monostearate.webp\">\r\n<meta name=\"twitter:description\" content=\"MLA Group is a leading manufacturer & supplier of Sorbitan Monosearate, we are one of the best exporters of SMS in the world offering the best price.\" />\r\n<meta name=\"twitter:creator\" content=\"MLA Group\">\r\n\r\n', 'product-image/sorbitan-monostearate.webp', NULL, '', 'Unpublished', '<h2>Sorbitan Monostearate (SMS)</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>MLA Group is a leading Sorbitan Monostearate manufacturers in India with over several decades of experience in the chemical industry. Our strong global chemical resource capabilities, professional control quality management system, and unparalleled customer support provide you with high-quality chemical products for industrial production. That&#39;s the reason MLA is a Star Export House with exports to over 50 countries.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Our company follows a stringent 3-tier Quality Control System and FEMA ensuring the safety, consistency, and reliability of our product. Our reputation precedes us making us one of the most sought-after Sorbitan Monostearate manufacturers in the World.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Sorbitan Monostearate - Product Description</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Sorbitan monostearate is a synthetic ester made by the reaction of Sorbitan with stearic acid under controlled conditions. SMS is used in the manufacture of food and healthcare products as a non-ionic surfactant with emulsifying, dispersing, and wetting properties. It is also employed to create synthetic fibers, metal machining fluid, and as a brightener in the leather industry. It is used in yeast manufacturing to protect the yeast from excess drying and also helps rehydrate the yeast cells.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Sorbitan monostearate (abbreviation SMS), or Span 60, is an emulsifier esterified from Sorbitan and stearic acid with the European food additive number E491. This ingredient is mostly used in baking yeast by improving the activity of instant dry yeast when the yeast is rehydrated before use.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Appearance and properties</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>A white to yellow waxy bead or flake with a slight characteristic smell.</p>\r\n\r\n<h4>HYDROPHILIC-LIPOPHILIC BALANCE (HLB)</h4>\r\n\r\n<p>With the HLB value of 4.7, meaning it is lipophilic and soluble in oil instead of water. It will form W/O (water-in-oil) type emulsion, and it is a strong emulsifying dispersion and has a wetting effect. A white to yellow waxy bead or flake with a slight characteristic smell.</p>\r\n\r\n<h4>HYDROPHILIC-LIPOPHILIC BALANCE (HLB)</h4>\r\n\r\n<p>With the HLB value of 4.7, meaning it is lipophilic and soluble in oil instead of water. It will form W/O (water-in-oil) type emulsion, and it is a strong emulsifying dispersion and has a wetting effect</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Leading Sorbitan Monostearate suppliers in India</h2>\r\n\r\n<h3>Our Advantage</h3>\r\n\r\n<h4>100% genuine products</h4>\r\n\r\n<p>We produce an authentic veg origin high-quality Sorbitan Monostearate. All types of compliances and quality assurance certifications are available.</p>\r\n\r\n<h4>Prompt responses</h4>\r\n\r\n<p>We believe in fast and timely responses and are able to provide you with all the required information in a short period of time.</p>\r\n\r\n<h4>Competitive prices</h4>\r\n\r\n<p>While we provide high-quality Sorbitan Monostearate, we also make sure that we provide the best market prices for our products. This is made possible by our high economies of scale for various esters.</p>\r\n\r\n<h4>Excellent Customer Support</h4>\r\n\r\n<p>We aim to provide the best sales and after-sales services to our customers, backed with technical and commercial support.</p>\r\n\r\n<h4>Fast and timely delivery</h4>\r\n\r\n<p>We have an efficient logistics system in place to look over the delivery of products and also make sure of their safe transit.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>FAQs</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Answered by the leading Sorbitan Monostearate exporters in India</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Is the Sorbitan Monostearate manufactured by you Halal?</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Yes, as the leading Sorbitan Monostearate manufacturers and exporters in the world, we provide a synthetic ester that would be halal complying with the Muslim policy as the fatty acid stearic acid is derived from vegetable oils instead of animal origins.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Is Sorbitan Monostearate manufactured by you Vegan?</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Yes, it is vegan as the raw material stearic acid is derived from vegetable oils and the manufacturing process is without the use of animal matter or products derived from animal origin.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>What is the shelf life of Sorbitan Monostearate manufactured by you? Also, what is the legal status on the same?</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Shelf Life:</strong>&nbsp;Sorbitan Monostearate manufactured at MLA Group has a shelf life of one year from the date of production, if stored under mentioned storage conditions and unopened packaging.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Legal Status:</strong>Our SMS meets the specifications fixed by FAO/WHO and the EU. However, users must check for permissibility for the use of this product in foods in their own country as the food laws may differ in each country.</p>\r\n', '', '<h2>Uses of Sorbitan monostearate</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>As leading suppliers and exporters of Sorbitan Monostearate in the world, we have been serving many foods and other industries with absolute consistency in quality at a reasonable cost.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Food Applications</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Sorbitan monostearate or SMS is used as an emulsifier, commonly together with polysorbates to keep water and oil mixed in many food products.<br />\r\nIt is commonly used in instant fat and oil emulsions, desserts, food supplements, cake, spread, margarine, coffee whiteners.</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Dry yeast: maintain the moisture, increase the shelf life of dry yeast, and help the rehydration of yeast cells before blended with other dough ingredients.</li>\r\n	<li>Ice cream: promote emulsification of dairy fat, prevent the formation of ice crystals, and improve the mouthfeel.</li>\r\n	<li>Margarine: improve emulsion stability and reduce sandiness.</li>\r\n	<li>Whipping cream: improve foam volume and contribute to a nice and stiff foam.</li>\r\n	<li>Bread &amp; Cake: increase the loaf volume and improve the texture of bread and cake.</li>\r\n	<li>Confections and chocolate: stabilize the emulsion of oils and fats.</li>\r\n	<li>Flavored fermented milk products.</li>\r\n	<li>Beverage whiteners.</li>\r\n	<li>Fat and oil emulsions.</li>\r\n	<li>Sugar confectionery.</li>\r\n	<li>Chewing gum.</li>\r\n	<li>Decorations, coatings, and fillings.</li>\r\n	<li>Fine bakery wares.</li>\r\n	<li>Emulsified sauces.</li>\r\n	<li>Desserts.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h3>Non-food applications</h3>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Pharmaceuticals &amp; Cosmetics</li>\r\n	<li>Plastic food wrap</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '2024-09-27 13:59:16', '2025-06-09 13:22:27'),
