large number of PVC manufacturing companies across the world.</p>\r\n\r\n<p bis_size=\"{&quot;x&quot;:20,&quot;y&quot;:95,&quot;w&quot;:1127,&quot;h&quot;:41,&quot;abs_x&quot;:306,&quot;abs_y&quot;:1700}\">We are committed to providing our customers best quality products at competitive prices. With fast and reliable supplies, we have grown into the most reliable brand in the industry, established trust based relations with leading PVC processors worldwide, and have become a&nbsp;leading PVC heat stabilizers suppliers and exporters in the world.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2 bis_size=\"{&quot;x&quot;:20,&quot;y&quot;:153,&quot;w&quot;:1127,&quot;h&quot;:23,&quot;abs_x&quot;:306,&quot;abs_y&quot;:1758}\">The product - PVC heat stabilizers</h2>\r\n\r\n<p bis_size=\"{&quot;x&quot;:20,&quot;y&quot;:192,&quot;w&quot;:1127,&quot;h&quot;:62,&quot;abs_x&quot;:306,&quot;abs_y&quot;:1797}\">We provide PVC Heat Stabilizers (one packs - lead based &amp; calcium-zinc non-toxic) in powder and flakes form. In PVC Processing (extrusion, injection molding, etc.), the polymer is subjected to a high temperature which can lead to burning (degradation or breaking of polymer chains). Heat stabilizers are lead compounds that are added to prevent burning by capturing and inactivating the labile chlorine that is produced on heating of PVC.</p>\r\n\r\n<p bis_size=\"{&quot;x&quot;:20,&quot;y&quot;:268,&quot;w&quot;:1127,&quot;h&quot;:41,&quot;abs_x&quot;:306,&quot;abs_y&quot;:1873}\">Conventionally, a combination of three chemicals, TBLS, DBLS, and LS (Tribasic lead sulphate, dibasic Lead stearate, and Lead stearate) were used as heat stabilizers along with&nbsp;Calcium Stearate&nbsp;as a co-stabilizer. MLA Group is the leading manufacture of these&nbsp;single stabilizers&nbsp;in the highest purity and performance.</p>\r\n\r\n<p bis_size=\"{&quot;x&quot;:20,&quot;y&quot;:322,&quot;w&quot;:1127,&quot;h&quot;:41,&quot;abs_x&quot;:306,&quot;abs_y&quot;:1927}\">Nowadays, one&ndash;pack stabilizer is used in place of the three chemicals as a heat stabilizer. It is made by in-situ reaction of lead oxide with stearic acid along with many other components like waxes, antioxidants, inorganic stabilizers etc, which were not there in the conventional system of single stabilizers above.</p>\r\n\r\n<p bis_size=\"{&quot;x&quot;:20,&quot;y&quot;:377,&quot;w&quot;:1127,&quot;h&quot;:20,&quot;abs_x&quot;:306,&quot;abs_y&quot;:1982}\">Its performance depends on two things:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul bis_size=\"{&quot;x&quot;:20,&quot;y&quot;:411,&quot;w&quot;:1127,&quot;h&quot;:41,&quot;abs_x&quot;:306,&quot;abs_y&quot;:2016}\">\r\n	<li bis_size=\"{&quot;x&quot;:60,&quot;y&quot;:411,&quot;w&quot;:1047,&quot;h&quot;:20,&quot;abs_x&quot;:346,&quot;abs_y&quot;:2016}\">&nbsp;the lead oxide content which provides stabilization by deactivating the chloride radical formed during heated melt processing of PVC during extrusion and</li>\r\n	<li bis_size=\"{&quot;x&quot;:60,&quot;y&quot;:431,&quot;w&quot;:1047,&quot;h&quot;:20,&quot;abs_x&quot;:346,&quot;abs_y&quot;:2036}\">by providing lubrication so that the residence time inside the screw extruder (heated zone) is reduced, so less deterioration is there.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p bis_size=\"{&quot;x&quot;:20,&quot;y&quot;:465,&quot;w&quot;:1127,&quot;h&quot;:20,&quot;abs_x&quot;:306,&quot;abs_y&quot;:2070}\">MLA Group produces a dozen of popular one-pack grades with different lead contents as well as over a hundred customized grades.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2 bis_size=\"{&quot;x&quot;:20,&quot;y&quot;:502,&quot;w&quot;:1127,&quot;h&quot;:23,&quot;abs_x&quot;:306,&quot;abs_y&quot;:2107}\">Industries utilizing PVC stabilizers</h2>\r\n\r\n<p bis_size=\"{&quot;x&quot;:20,&quot;y&quot;:542,&quot;w&quot;:1127,&quot;h&quot;:20,&quot;abs_x&quot;:306,&quot;abs_y&quot;:2147}\">Being one of the leading suppliers of PVC stabilizers, we offer services to various sectors. A few of them are:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul bis_size=\"{&quot;x&quot;:20,&quot;y&quot;:576,&quot;w&quot;:1127,&quot;h&quot;:187,&quot;abs_x&quot;:306,&quot;abs_y&quot;:2181}\">\r\n	<li bis_size=\"{&quot;x&quot;:60,&quot;y&quot;:576,&quot;w&quot;:1047,&quot;h&quot;:20,&quot;abs_x&quot;:346,&quot;abs_y&quot;:2181}\">Construction: These PVC stabilizers help pipes and fittings to be long-lasting at high temperatures and in other harsh weather conditions.</li>\r\n	<li bis_size=\"{&quot;x&quot;:60,&quot;y&quot;:596,&quot;w&quot;:1047,&quot;h&quot;:20,&quot;abs_x&quot;:346,&quot;abs_y&quot;:2201}\">Automotive: They enhance heat and ultraviolet light resistance stabilizers in elements, including dashboards, interiors, etc.</li>\r\n	<li bis_size=\"{&quot;x&quot;:60,&quot;y&quot;:617,&quot;w&quot;:1047,&quot;h&quot;:20,&quot;abs_x&quot;:346,&quot;abs_y&quot;:2222}\">Food and Medical Packaging: Manufacturers use stabilizers for flexible materials to protect food and medications from physical and chemical threats.</li>\r\n	<li bis_size=\"{&quot;x&quot;:60,&quot;y&quot;:638,&quot;w&quot;:1047,&quot;h&quot;:41,&quot;abs_x&quot;:346,&quot;abs_y&quot;:2243}\">Electrical &amp; Electronics: PVC stabilizers improve the functioning of insulation and sheathing used in the construction of wires as well as cables due to their great thermal and fire properties.</li>\r\n	<li bis_size=\"{&quot;x&quot;:60,&quot;y&quot;:680,&quot;w&quot;:1047,&quot;h&quot;:41,&quot;abs_x&quot;:346,&quot;abs_y&quot;:2285}\">Healthcare:&nbsp;In the healthcare segment, PVC Stabilizers are employed in the manufacturing of articles including blood bags, IV tubes, and oxygen masks. Thus, it serves to meet the requirements of flexibility, safety, and the ability to pass through the sterilization processes.</li>\r\n	<li bis_size=\"{&quot;x&quot;:60,&quot;y&quot;:721,&quot;w&quot;:1047,&quot;h&quot;:41,&quot;abs_x&quot;:346,&quot;abs_y&quot;:2326}\">Agriculture:&nbsp;There is a requirement for stabilizers to be used in the manufacture of greenhouse films, irrigation pipes, and other agricultural equipment that require harsh exposure to UV