stantly growing, making us a&nbsp;leading PVC heat stabilizers exporters in India and the world.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2 bis_size=\"{&quot;x&quot;:20,&quot;y&quot;:1523,&quot;w&quot;:1127,&quot;h&quot;:23,&quot;abs_x&quot;:306,&quot;abs_y&quot;:3128}\">FAQs</h2>\r\n\r\n<p bis_size=\"{&quot;x&quot;:20,&quot;y&quot;:1563,&quot;w&quot;:1127,&quot;h&quot;:20,&quot;abs_x&quot;:306,&quot;abs_y&quot;:3168}\"><strong bis_size=\"{&quot;x&quot;:20,&quot;y&quot;:1566,&quot;w&quot;:386,&quot;h&quot;:14,&quot;abs_x&quot;:306,&quot;abs_y&quot;:3171}\">What are the benefits of using One pack PVC Heat Stabilizers?</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p bis_size=\"{&quot;x&quot;:20,&quot;y&quot;:1597,&quot;w&quot;:1127,&quot;h&quot;:41,&quot;abs_x&quot;:306,&quot;abs_y&quot;:3202}\">There are several benefits of using our one pack PVC Heat Stabilizers that include: reduced labour cost, reduced handling losses, reduced inventory, a better homogenous mixture from processing. We provide PVC Heat Stabilizers (one pack- lead-based) in powder and flakes form, that can be modified as per the needs and requirements of the customers.</p>\r\n\r\n<p bis_size=\"{&quot;x&quot;:20,&quot;y&quot;:1651,&quot;w&quot;:1127,&quot;h&quot;:20,&quot;abs_x&quot;:306,&quot;abs_y&quot;:3256}\"><strong bis_size=\"{&quot;x&quot;:20,&quot;y&quot;:1654,&quot;w&quot;:333,&quot;h&quot;:14,&quot;abs_x&quot;:306,&quot;abs_y&quot;:3259}\">What is the preferred dosage of PVC Heat Stabilizers?</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p bis_size=\"{&quot;x&quot;:20,&quot;y&quot;:1685,&quot;w&quot;:1127,&quot;h&quot;:62,&quot;abs_x&quot;:306,&quot;abs_y&quot;:3290}\">The dosage of stabilizers per hundred parts of resin ( PVC ) is 2.5-3.5 phr in pipes and 3.0 to 12.0 phr in different types of cables, but it depends on lead content in stabilizer and the filler used by PVC product manufacturer. If the filler is more, the dosage required is more. Detailed application knowledge and formula/recipe for any customer can be provided by our technical services managers.</p>\r\n\r\n<p bis_size=\"{&quot;x&quot;:20,&quot;y&quot;:1760,&quot;w&quot;:1127,&quot;h&quot;:20,&quot;abs_x&quot;:306,&quot;abs_y&quot;:3365}\"><strong bis_size=\"{&quot;x&quot;:20,&quot;y&quot;:1764,&quot;w&quot;:391,&quot;h&quot;:14,&quot;abs_x&quot;:306,&quot;abs_y&quot;:3369}\">Why should I purchase PVC Heat Stabilizers From MLA Group?</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p bis_size=\"{&quot;x&quot;:20,&quot;y&quot;:1794,&quot;w&quot;:1127,&quot;h&quot;:62,&quot;abs_x&quot;:306,&quot;abs_y&quot;:3399}\">At MLA Group, we manufacture products under a controlled environment and with high precision, strict quality controls, and standardized procedures to bring you a premium product every single time. Due to our huge capacity and aggressive approach, our prices are most economical. We are a&nbsp;leading PVC heat stabilizers suppliers in India&nbsp;who is committed to continuous improvement through R&amp;D, to serve the customers with quality products at lower costs through higher productivity and unmatched customer service.</p>\r\n\r\n<p bis_size=\"{&quot;x&quot;:20,&quot;y&quot;:1870,&quot;w&quot;:1127,&quot;h&quot;:62,&quot;abs_x&quot;:306,&quot;abs_y&quot;:3475}\"><strong bis_size=\"{&quot;x&quot;:20,&quot;y&quot;:1873,&quot;w&quot;:298,&quot;h&quot;:14,&quot;abs_x&quot;:306,&quot;abs_y&quot;:3478}\">Are there eco-friendly PVC stabilizers available?</strong><br bis_size=\"{&quot;x&quot;:318,&quot;y&quot;:1873,&quot;w&quot;:0,&quot;h&quot;:14,&quot;abs_x&quot;:604,&quot;abs_y&quot;:3478}\" />\r\nAny ideal service provider must offer sustainability. Thus, being among the top PVC stabilizer manufacturers in India, we offer eco-friendly options like calcium-zinc and organic-based stabilizers. These comply with environmental standards while maintaining high performance.</p>\r\n\r\n<p bis_size=\"{&quot;x&quot;:20,&quot;y&quot;:1945,&quot;w&quot;:1127,&quot;h&quot;:41,&quot;abs_x&quot;:306,&quot;abs_y&quot;:3550}\"><strong bis_size=\"{&quot;x&quot;:20,&quot;y&quot;:1948,&quot;w&quot;:286,&quot;h&quot;:14,&quot;abs_x&quot;:306,&quot;abs_y&quot;:3553}\">How is the quality of PVC stabilizers ensured?</strong><br bis_size=\"{&quot;x&quot;:306,&quot;y&quot;:1948,&quot;w&quot;:0,&quot;h&quot;:14,&quot;abs_x&quot;:592,&quot;abs_y&quot;:3553}\" />\r\nBeing among the leading PVC stabilizers exporters, we conduct rigorous testing of raw materials and products, adhering to international standards to ensure consistency and safety.</p>\r\n', '', '<h2><meta charset=\"utf-8\" /><b id=\"docs-internal-guid-b93dd31d-7fff-3f23-94f2-62fe9bd6c0d6\">Application of PVC stabilizers</b></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Tribasic lead sulphate, Dibasic lead stearate, Lead stearate are used as heat stabilizers while processing PVC items so that they do not get burnt/degraded due to high temperatures used in processing.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Our one packs are a combination of above and other additives such as anti-oxidants etc., all put together in one product which provides ease of handling while its function is the same as above: to provide heat stability to PVC.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>At MLA Group, we have developed a full range of PVC Stabilizers to be used in various industries with different applications that include:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>PVC Rigid Pipes &amp; Conduits,</li>\r\n	<li>&nbsp;PVC Fittings,</li>\r\n	<li>&nbsp;PVC Wires and Cables,</li>\r\n	<li>&nbsp;PVC Floor covering,</li>\r\n	<li>&nbsp;PVC Soil Pipes for gases and liquids.</li>\r\n	<li>&nbsp;Other products such as shoe compounds, suction hoses, gasket sheets, etc.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '2024-12-02 11:04:26', '2025-06-23 12:36:50'),
